Subject: [Caml-list] OCaml Platform - Mailing List

Dear caml-list,

As some of you may be aware from the Consortium meeting, there's an ongoing=
 project to create an OCaml Platform.  The Platform will combine the core O=
Caml compiler distribution from INRIA with a comprehensive, coherent set of=
 libraries, tools, documentation, and other resources.  For example, the OP=
AM package manager will play a central role in both packaging and distribut=
ion, as well as supporting continuous integration testing.

This email is to let you know that we've set up a mailing list to discuss t=
he Platform (platform@lists.ocaml.org), and those who are interested can fo=
llow the day-to-day discussions there [1].  Any important announcements, in=
cluding releases, would also be copied to the caml-list when appropriate, s=
o you don't need to join if you only want updates.

Best wishes,
Amir

[1] http://lists.ocaml.org/listinfo/platform=
